&lt;p&gt;Backed by top regional and global VCs, &lt;strong&gt;BRKZ is Saudi Arabia’s fastest-growing construction-tech startup&lt;/strong&gt;. Our web platform, mobile apps and WhatsApp channels give contractors instant access to 7,000+ building-material SKUs from 1,100+ vetted suppliers, with quotes in minutes and buy-now-pay-later financing built in. In just two years we have on-boarded 850+ contracting companies, supported giga-projects such as &lt;strong&gt;NEOM&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;King Salman Park&lt;/strong&gt;, and scaled RFQs to $350 million while keeping positive unit economics.&lt;/p&gt;
