&lt;p&gt;As a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Credit Risk Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;you will be responsible for safeguarding the company’s financial health by identifying, assessing, and mitigating credit risks across our diverse portfolio. You’ll play a pivotal role in shaping risk strategies that balance innovation with responsibility, ensuring that BRkz.com continues to grow sustainably while protecting our customers and stakeholders. This is a high-impact role that requires strong analytical skills, regulatory knowledge, and the ability to collaborate across teams in a fast-paced fintech environment.&lt;/p&gt;
